overview: Henry is good, Henry is bad, but when it comes to footage that he finds, the end result is horrendous. Where does he find these tapes? Why does he keep making them? Why does he keep uploading them? Will the right authorities ever figure out what is going on? These questions will be asked because once you go LIVE, the followers will THRIVE.
title: Paranoia Tapes 6: 06:06:06
